data.description: Fantastic traditional ranch home! VA ASSUMABLE LOAN at 4.125% interest rate. Beautifully painted kitchen cabinets & pantry, stainless steel appliances and hardwood floors. Half bath and laundry room conveniently located between kitchen and garage. Newer LVP floor, built-in bookcase and gas fireplace makes the living room warm and inviting. Master bedroom large enough for oversized furniture with en suite includes double bowl vanity, shower, deep linen closet, walk-in closet and a 2nd closet. Basement family room, office, and a 4th bedroom provides ample room for recreation and work space. Mobile bar w/two stools stays. 4th bedroom with double closet has its own private bath, tiled shower. Non conforming 5th bedroom has adjoining storage closet, or easily converted into a huge walk-in closet. A special feature that stands out is the enclosed back porch to enjoy the wooded scenery and back yard.
